node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Fronzak 😈 in Orlando, Florida with @staysickthreads.

node.text: Our 10-year anniversary collection JUST went live on our website! We worked really hard to bring this to life and created some really cool pieces. We even brought back a couple of our ORIGINAL designs when we first started in 2011. Thank you for all of the support you've given us the past 10 years, we appreciate you more than words can describe. Now hit that link in my bio & pick up your favorite items before they're sold out! 🤘🏼🤘🏼🤘🏼

node.text: Cheers to one of the best weekends of my life ✨ My band released a brand new album and now I'm on an island with the people I love breaking open coconuts 🥥💞

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Fronzak 😈 in Orlando, Florida with @attila_ga. May be an image of text.

node.text: Today is the official release of our brand new album #Closure. We put 2 years of hard work into creating this album and I'm confident you'll enjoy what we made for you. We all faced a lot of hardships during this time period, both on a personal level and a worldly level, and you'll certainly feel that in some of the songs. Don't get me wrong, we still have the party bangers and we still have the heavy slammers, but overall this album is a diverse experience. You will find songs reminiscent of Rage & About That Life, and you will also find songs that are completely different. Please take a moment of your day to download #Closure and give it a full listen and let me know what you think below! 🖤👇🏼
